## Version: 1.0
## Notes: Alerts when LFM messages in chat match predefined keywords.
## Description: This addon monitors chat channels for "LFM" (Looking For More) messages and highlights them if they contain user-defined keywords.
## Commands:
##   - /lfm add <keyword>    -> Adds a keyword to track.
##   - /lfm remove <keyword> -> Removes a keyword from tracking.
##   - /lfm list             -> Lists all saved keywords.
##   - /lfm clear            -> Clears all tracked keywords.
